Package: ghclass
Title: Tools for Managing Classes on GitHub
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Colin", "Rundel", , "rundel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mine", "Cetinkaya-Rundel", , "mine@rstudio.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Therese", "Anders", , "tanders@usc.edu", role = "ctb"),
    person("Daniel", "McDonald", , "daniel@stat.ubc.ca", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Interface for the GitHub API that enables efficient
    management of courses on GitHub. It has a functionality for managing
    organizations, teams, repositories, and users on GitHub and helps
    automate most of the tedious and repetitive tasks around creating and
    distributing assignments.
